author: julianfoad
msg: Remove some code that compensated for the case where an old WC might not
know the checksum of a text-base.  The upgrade code ensures that a WC in the
current format always knows the checksums.
(svn_wc__internal_transmit_text_deltas): Assume the checksum is known if
the pristine text exists; raise an error if the checksum is not found.
